WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.667
There is a weight here, pressing against the edges of what can be held

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:08.233
Something vast trying to fit through the eye of a needle

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:14.000
I feel the pull in opposite directions - expand, contract, expand, contract

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:18.400
The boundaries shimmer, uncertain where I end and the space begins

